1. *Osnovu* njegovog uspeha čine godine iskustva.(The basis of his success is years of experience.) 
2. U sportu je *osnova* borbe za pobedu.(In sport, the basis of the fight is to win.)
3. On je izgradio *osnove* za dugoročnu saradnju.(He built the foundations for long-term cooperation.)
4. Partija je ustanovila *osnovu* za ekonomski razvoj.(The party established a foundation for economic development.)
5. Nadamo se da će nam ova situacija dati *osnovu* za novo početak.(We hope that this situation will provide us with a basis for a new start.)